    "updated_at": "2016-11-21T01:39:23Z",
    "body": "Not commenting on supporting a linux auto-updating mechanism or Electron's position on it (Someone else will I'm sure).  But I felt I had to point out regarding one of your questions.\r\n\r\n> Being Electron based on Chrome, how is it possible that it can't auto-update on Linux, given the fact that Chrome can?\r\n\r\nAlthough you are correct and Electron is based on Chromium, the auto-update mechanisms provided by Electron aren't the update mechanisms from Chromium.  They are in fact different for different OS's.\r\n\r\nOn windows we use https://github.com/Squirrel/Squirrel.Windows and on macOS we use https://github.com/Squirrel/Squirrel.Mac"
  },
